nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.31

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.31 is the thirty-first issue of the sixth volume of Star Wars Comic UK. It was published on March 8, 2012 and comes with lightsaber pencils. It also contains the segments Top Lightsaber Duels! and an episode guide of Shadow Warrior.
The comic included the comic strip "Deadly Droid."
